Yakundanye n'umuraperi, J Molley kumurusha imyaka 10 aho ibihuha byatangiriye mu Kwakira 2019. <ref>https://www.iol.co.za/entertainment/celebrity-news/local/tweeps-weigh-in-on-khanya-mkangisa-and-j-molleys-10-year-age-gap-4851d9f4-eaf3-43d4-a0a3-7e5e1871735d</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka 14, yinjiye kuri tereviziyo maze aba umunyamakuru wa Yo YV. Yakomeje gukora mu musaruro imyaka itatu. Hanyuma yimutse kugirango yerekane siyanse ''yubumenyi yitwa Knock Knock'' . Mu 2004, yerekanye televiziyo ye ya mbere ''yakinnye muri serie Mthunzini.'' ''Com'' . Nyuma yaje gukina muri ''Lab1'' nka 'Refilwe' na ''Ugugu noAndile'' . Nkumunyamakuru, yakiriye igitaramo cyo kubyina 'Shield Teen'. Hagati aho, yagaragaye cyane mu bitaramo bizwi cyane muri ''Zone 14'' muri 2011 na ''Intersexions'' muri 2012. Muri 2012, yakinnye muri BBC ''yise Mad Dogs III'' afite uruhare 'Anna'. Hanyuma muri 2013, yinjiye mu bakinnyi basanzwe ba serial ''Zabalaza'' akina 'Mpilo'. <ref>https://legends.co.za/model/khanya-mkangisa/</ref>

Muri 2019, yerekanye bwa mbere nk'umuhanzi wa DJ maze akora ibitaramo muri Jozi to Quilox weekend weekend i Lagos, muri [[Nijeriya]] . <ref>https://www.news24.com/channel/the-juice/news/pics-khanya-mkangisa-is-in-nigeria-for-the-first-time-and-she-loves-it-20190911</ref> Muri 2020, yagaragaye bwa mbere muri sabune izwi cyane ''Muvhango'' afite uruhare rwa 'Mbali'. <ref>https://www.peoplemagazine.co.za/celebrity-news/local-celebrities/khanya-mkangisa-bags-new-role-on-muvhango/</ref>

